---

<section class="py-24 md:py-40 bg-warm-stone grain-overlay">
  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Left: Dramatic year + headline -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <p class="font-display text-8xl sm:text-9xl text-warm-white/10 leading-none select-none reveal">
          2000
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-6 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-warm-white leading-[1.05] reveal reveal-delay-1">
          Then the dot-com<br />
          bubble burst.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: The weight of the moment -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-warm-white/70 leading-relaxed max-w-xl reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <p>
            The tech economy collapsed. Colleagues lost jobs. My income
            was cut, but I kept mine. Several of them weren't as fortunate
            &mdash; they lost their homes.
          </p>
          <p>
            They'd bought at the top of their approval. No margin. No cushion.
            When income dropped, there was nowhere to go.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- The contrast moment -->
        <div class="mt-12 reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="border-l-2 border-l-storehouse-400 pl-8 py-2">
            <p class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-warm-white leading-snug">
              I wasn't rich. But I was okay.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-storehouse-400/80">
              That wasn't luck. That was Bob.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
